summary.problem: User requests access to ABARES historical data including estimate evolution dataset and official SND and production data.
summary.solution: The ABARES datasets can be accessed on the platform using the dataset identifiers sucden-27ba62ab-8a80-4184-a1bd-836daa59ae8a and sucden-d95185b7-1e44-457a-895c-e05793f27f84. Users should look for these dataset codes within the platform to find the estimate evolution dataset and official SND and production data.
